Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的博客发布的一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在仍然缺少一些图像。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在让我们学习如何使用 HTML &lt;img&gt;元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，如果我们查看演示页面，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们注意到这里有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,种重要的图像。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我们这里有这张大图，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪种说明了博客文章。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们也有这张作者的照片。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在让我们开始在这里合并这张图片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入我们的博客。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，图像当然在我们的项目文件夹中。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，他们附带了启动文件。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将在这里包括的一个，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个帖子图片。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以当你双击时你会看到，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以当你打开这个文件时，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么VSCode实际上是能够显示图像文件的，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.35,0:00:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且没有任何问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:01:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们想要这个图片就在这个作者之后。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以基本上图像是一个障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文章开头之间，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.97,0:01:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和页面的其余部分，所以顶部。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我想这里，实际上这里的标题，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这个&lt;h2&gt;元素应该在作者之前。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们把它移到这里。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，所以首先，当然，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我们在这里一样，需要来实际的标题。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以标题元素，只有作者，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这里的图像。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，但无论如何，让我们现在包含 &lt;img&gt;元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说一次，就在这一段之后，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想要包含这张图片。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就像任何其他元素一样，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从这样写开始。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:01:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在请记住我实际上是如何告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本节的第一讲中，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,&lt;img&gt; element 是一个特殊的元素，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为它没有任何内容，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此它也没有结束标签。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反，我们所做的是简单地添加斜线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在元素的最后。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你可能想知道我们是否在这里没有指定任何内容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于这个&lt;img&gt;元素，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 HTML 如何知道它应该显示哪个元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个很好的问题，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这给我们带来了 HTML 中的一些新东西，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是属性。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以属性基本上是数据片段，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以用它来描述元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以HTML中有很多不同的属性，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中之一是 &lt;source&gt;属性。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们现在感兴趣的。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以&lt;来源&gt;像这样，SRC，然后是一个相等的，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们需要这样的双引号，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们可以简单地指定图像的名称。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请记住，那是 post-img.jpg。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们只写post-img，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们甚至可以让 VSCode 自动完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的代码，比如点击这里，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或下降，实际上这没有用。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果我们只是在这里输入，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这样就可以了。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以再次，我们可以手动编写它，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者只是使用 VSCode 的自动完成功能。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上就是这样，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是v我们需要的任何基础知识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了显示图像。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果我们现在重新加载它，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会看到它确实在这里。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，所以再一次，让我们快速回顾一下。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有指定图片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个元素中使用一些内容。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反，我们需要做的是指定一个属性。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种情况下，它是 &lt;source&gt;属性。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住一个属性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上就像一个数据，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一条描述这个元素的信息。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这里我们描述源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浏览器基本上应该从中读取图像。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在，除了&lt;source&gt;属性，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以为图像指定其他属性，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不应该跳过的一个是 alt 属性。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们这样写，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alt 代表替代文本。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以基本上我们需要在这里指定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一些应该描述图像内容的文本。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出于各种原因，这非常重要。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中之一是它将允许搜索引擎，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如谷歌浏览器，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正了解图像中的内容，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有这个描述，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索引擎真的不知道知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图像实际上是关于什么的。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其次，也许更重要的是，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是通过指定图像的描述，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也可以让盲人使用网站。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以使用屏幕阅读器的用户
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会看到图像，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他们将拥有屏幕阅读器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阅读替代文本，以便对他们进行描述。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以永远不要跳过这个属性。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是写一个好的描述是非常重要的。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在这里，假设这里的这张图片是HTML代码
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在屏幕上。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，现在这在视觉上不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上我们在这里看到的。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们重新加载，除非图像出于某种原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如，假设我们在这里忘记了 G。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在这个图像路径是完全错误的。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果我们现在重新加载，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么浏览器将无法找到图像，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但相反，它将做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在这里打印我们的描述。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们在此处提供的屏幕上的 HTML 代码。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，这实际上是替代文本的另一个用例。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们把它放回去，我们实际上还没有完成。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们可以在这里指定更多的属性，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种情况下，这非常重要。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是图像宽度和图像高度。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在这张图片有点太大了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们将其宽度指定为 500 像素，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心这 500 像素是什么意思，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者确切地说是一个像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦我们到达 CSS 部分，我们将更多地讨论这一点，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在让我们只写宽度，并将其设置为 500，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后让我们看看，好吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:07:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在它把图像缩放到 500 的宽度，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它还自动保持纵横比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的图像。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，但我们也可以指定。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以除了宽度，我们还可以指定高度，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是200。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这一点，因为我知道图像尺寸。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果我们再次打开它，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里看到原始图像是一千乘四百。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，如果我将宽度指定为 500，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是一千的一半，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这里的高度也必须是400的一半，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那将是200。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，现在看起来应该一样了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此，但当然，如果我想要的话，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如，我可以把它做成一个正方形，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后会完全扭曲图像，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我们在这里看到的那样。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我们不想要那个，所以把它放回去，我们开始吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，这就是我们包含图像的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成 HTML 文档。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这里的这个只是我们想要的第一个。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一张图片是这个作者图片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在此作者段落的上方就在这里。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们现在想要的形象就是这个，劳拉·琼斯，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们希望它的高度和宽度为 50 像素。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，所以我有另一个挑战给你。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我想让你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是包括我刚才给你看的这张图片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个地方你自己。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，花点时间，暂停视频，
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并包含这个 50 x 50 像素的图像。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我会在一分钟内回到这里并提供解决方案。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，所以希望你能在那里多练习。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以形象，我将立即开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写属性，最后我会，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关闭元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在这里我们想要劳拉琼斯，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我只需按 Enter 或 Return
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此处自动完成文件名。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是替代文字，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设这是劳拉·琼斯的头像，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是乔纳斯，而是一个高度，又是这里，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在可以按 Enter 或返回以自动完成此操作。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我实际上希望你写这些属性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己动手，让它们进入你的脑海。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这真的很重要。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以高度和宽度为 50，仅此而已。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我们关闭元素，保存它，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 Prettier 做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这些属性中的每一个放在一行中，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这使它很容易看到。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实让我们关闭我们的侧边栏，让我们看看。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们开始。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这是劳拉琼斯现在的照片。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错，不错，进步很大。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在我们知道图像是如何工作的，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及属性如何工作。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上我们可以指定属性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也适用于 HTML 中的其他一些元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个非常重要的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上是 HTML 元素本身。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在这个 HTML 元素中，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该指定我们用于此网页的语言。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以对于这个文件，我们可以通过说空白来做到这一点，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以指定 lang 属性，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在这种情况下，因为它是英语，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以将其设置为 EN，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对于其他语言，还有其他代码。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如，对于德语，可能只是 DE，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者对于葡萄牙语，它将是 PT。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有任何其他语言，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可以通过谷歌搜索轻松找到代码。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以而且实际上应该做的另一件事，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中需要属性是指定字符集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在文档中使用。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这是进入头脑的东西，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它是一条信息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,描述文档。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这里我们需要另一个新元素。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这被简单地称为meta，代表元数据。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以元数据意味着关于数据的数据。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在这里我们描述的是字符集，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们用这个属性来描述。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们说所说的字符应该是UTF-8，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这基本上是我们使用的所有简单字符
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在英语中。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这里的这个是这些元素中的另一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有结束标签，
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们就这样关闭它。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我不会花很多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这些元素，关于这类东西，
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为后来当你真正建立自己的页面时，
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这一切都会自动发生。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这只是为了向你展示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是另一种方式或另一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要一些属性，
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们需要为它指定一个值。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这里的UTF-8就是我们指定的值\N00:12:32,780 --> 00:12:34,83​​3\N对于这个字符集属性。\N\N234
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，是的，我想这就是本次讲座的内容了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，我们下期再见。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.47,0:00:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One thing that our blog post
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is still missing right now is some images.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so let's now learn how to use the HTML &lt;img&gt; element.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, if we check out the demo page,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then we notice that here we have two
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,kind of important images.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, we have this big image here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which kind of illustrates the blog post.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then we also have this photo here of the author.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so let's now start by incorporating this image here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,into our blog.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, the images are, of course, in our project folder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, they came with the starter files.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the one that we are going to include here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is this post image.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you see when you double click,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so when you open this file,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then VSCode is actually able to display image files,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.35,0:00:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and without any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:01:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we want this image right here after this author.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So basically the image serves as a barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,between the beginning of the article,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.97,0:01:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the rest of the page, so the top part.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I think that here, actually this title here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so this &lt;h2&gt; element should be before the author.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move that down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, so first, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,like we have it here, needs to come the actual title.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So the heading element, and only then the author,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then this image here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but anyway, let's now include the &lt;img&gt; element.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So again, right here after this paragraph,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we want to include this image.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So just like any other element,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we start by writing it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:01:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now remember how I actually told you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in the first lecture of this section,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that the &lt;img&gt; element is a special element,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and that's because it doesn't have any content,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and therefore it also doesn't have a closing tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, what we do is to simply add the slash
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,here at the very end of the element.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now you might wonder if we don't specify any content here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,for this &lt;img&gt; element,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then how will HTML know which element it should display.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that is an excellent question,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which brings us to something new in HTML,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which are attributes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So attributes are basically pieces of data,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which we can use to describe elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So there are lots of different attributes in HTML,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and one of them is the &lt;source&gt; attribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so that's the one we are interested in right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So &lt;source&gt; goes like this, SRC, and then an equal,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then we need double quotes like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then we can simply specify the name of the image.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So remember, that is post-img.jpg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so we just write post-img,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we could even allow VSCode to auto complete
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that code for us, like by clicking here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or going down, and actually that didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if we just hit enter here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then that would work just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So again, we can write it manually,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or just use VSCode's auto complete functionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's actually it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that's the very basics that we need
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in order to display an image.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if we reload this now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you will see that indeed here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Great, so again, let's just quickly recap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We did not specify the image
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,using some content in this element.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, what we needed to do was to specify an attribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And in this case, it's the &lt;source&gt; attribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And remember that an attribute
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is basically like a piece of data,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so a piece of information describing this element.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So here we are describing the source
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,from which the browser should basically read the image.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, besides the &lt;source&gt; attribute,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there are other attributes that we can specify for images,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and one that we should never skip is the alt attribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we write it like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and alt stands for alternative text.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So basically what we need to specify here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is some text that should describe what the image is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this is very important for various reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One of them is that it will allow search engines,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,such as Google Chrome,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to actually know what is in the image,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because without this description,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,search engines don't really have a know of knowing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what the image is actually about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And second, and probably even more important,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is that by specifying the description of the image,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we can also allow blind people to use a website.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So users who use a screen reader
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will not see the image,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but instead they will have the screen reader
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,read the alternative text, so the description to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So never skip this attribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's very important to always write a good description.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So here, let's say that this image here is HTML code
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on a screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now this will not visually change
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,actually what we see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's reload, unless the image for some reason
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,can not be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's say that we forgot the G here, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so now this image path is completely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if we now reload,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then the browser will not be able to find the image,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but instead, what it will do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is to then print our description here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the HTML code on a screen that we gave it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so that is actually another use case of the alt text.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put it back, and we are actually still not done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we can specify some more attributes here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which are quite important in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So the ones that I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are the image width and the image height.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So right now this image here is a little bit too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so let's specify its width to 500 pixels,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and don't worry yet about what these 500 pixels mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or exactly what a pixel is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will talk more about that once we reach the CSS section,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but for now let's just write width, and set it to 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then let's see, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:07:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So now it's scaled the image to a width of 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it automatically also maintained the aspect ratio
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of the image.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, but we can also specify that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So besides the width, we can also specify the height,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which should be 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I know that because I know the image dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if we open this up again,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you see here that the original image is a thousand by 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so if I specify the width as 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which is just half of a thousand,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then the height must also be half of 400 here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so that would be 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so that should now look the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it does, but of course, if I want it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could make it a square, for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which would then completely distort the image,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,just as we see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we don't want that, so put it back and here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Great, so this is how we include images
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,into an HTML document.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And to this one here was only the first one that we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The other image is this author image
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,right here above this author paragraph right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So the image that we want now is this one, Laura Jones,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we want it with a height and a width of 50 pixels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so I have another challenge for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what I want you to do this time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is to include this image that I just showed you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on your own right here in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so take a minute, and pause the video,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and include this image with 50 by 50 pixels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll be back here in a minute with the solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, so hopefully you got some more practice there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So image, and I will immediately start
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,writing the attributes, and I will then in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,close the element.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So here we want Laura Jones,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and now I will just hit enter or return
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to auto complete the file name here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then the alt text,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,let's say that this is a Headshot of Laura Jones,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and not Jonas, and a height, and here again,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we could now hit enter or return to auto complete this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I actually want you to write these attributes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,by yourself by hand, so that they get into your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So a height and a width of 50, and that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's close the element, give it a save,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then Prettier does this nice job
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of putting each of these attributes here in one line,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which makes it really easy to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually let's close down our sidebar here, and let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So here is that picture of Laura Jones now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, well done, nice progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So now we know how images work,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and how attributes work as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And actually we can specify attributes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,also on some other elements in HTML.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And one where this is very important
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is actually the HTML element itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So here in this HTML element,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we should specify the language that we use for this webpage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So for this document, and we can do that by saying blank,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so specifying the lang attribute,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then in this case, since it is English,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we can set it to EN,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but for other languages, there are other codes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For example, for German, just probably DE,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or for Portuguese, it would be PT.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if you have any other language,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you can just easily find out the code by Googling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Another thing that we can, and actually should do,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which needs attributes is to specify the character set
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that is used in the document.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that is something that goes into the head,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because it is a piece of information
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that describes the document.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So here we need another new element.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this is simply called meta, which stands for metadata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So metadata means data about the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so here we are describing that the character set,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which we describe by this attribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we say that the character said should be UTF-8,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which basically is all the simple characters that we use
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in the English language.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now this one here is another of these elements
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that doesn't have a closing tag,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and so we just close it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm not spending a whole lot of time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on these elements, and on this kind of stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because later when you actually built your own pages,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then this will all happen automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this was just to show you that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this is just another way or another place
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in which we need some attributes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,where we then need to specify a value for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So UTF-8 here is the value that we specified
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,for this character set attribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, and yeah, I think that's it for this lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, see you in the next one.